sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant User as User
  participant Web as Web/Admin app
  participant AuthProvider as AuthProvider
  participant AuthOTP as auth-otp function
  participant SupabaseAuth as Supabase Auth
  participant DB as Postgres
  participant Resend as Email provider

  User->>Web: Submit signup or login
  Web->>AuthProvider: signUp, signIn, or verifyOtp
  alt Signup with OTP
    AuthProvider->>AuthOTP: signup action
    AuthOTP->>SupabaseAuth: Create or update unconfirmed user
    AuthOTP->>DB: Store OTP record
    AuthOTP->>Resend: Send OTP email
    Resend-->>User: OTP email
    User->>Web: Enter OTP
    Web->>AuthProvider: verifyOtp
    AuthProvider->>AuthOTP: verify action
    AuthOTP->>DB: Validate unused OTP and profile
    AuthOTP->>SupabaseAuth: Confirm user metadata/state
  else Password login
    AuthProvider->>AuthOTP: validate-login-context
    AuthOTP->>SupabaseAuth: Admin user lookup
    AuthOTP-->>AuthProvider: Context result
    AuthProvider->>SupabaseAuth: signInWithPassword
    SupabaseAuth-->>AuthProvider: Session
  end
  AuthProvider->>DB: Load profile and roles
  DB-->>AuthProvider: Profile, role, plan data
  AuthProvider-->>Web: Authenticated app state

